CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 19, 1954, pg. 8 reads: "Thousands Attend Courier Home, Food Show...4. Refreshing non-fat dry milk was passed out from the Pet Milk Company booth by Miss Joyce Gibson. Wilbur Creelman, district manager supervises...-Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Wilbur Creelman and Joyce Gibson standing in Pet Milk promotional booth in the Hunt Armory for the 1954 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
